reviewText: I haven't received this movie but I have watched both of these movies and they are wonderful movies.
Great deal for Clint Eastwood fans. Two awesome movies for a good price.
I saw this movie when it first came out ; I liked it then and I like it even more now!!!! All the acting is superb...

I bought several of these for colleagues of my husbands after we traveled together to Alcatraz just before Christmas. It's a very old movie but fun to see the story of a site we had just toured, in a movie

Escape from Alcatraz is listed on the box as being 16x9 widescreen. It is not. Its actually letterbox which doesn't work with widescreen TVs. The picture is a tiny rectangle that has large black bars on the top bottom,  and both sides. I should've waited for it to come out on blu-ray.
